title: Zombie Driver: Immortal Edition llegará a Switch a finales de julio
body:
Zombie Driver: Immortal Edition es una loca mezcla de autos, velocidad, explosiones, sangre y zombies. Lucha en una campaña narrativa épica o ponte a prueba en los modos Slaughter y Blood Race. Involucra a jefes enormes, salve a sobrevivientes, conduzca vehículos locos como excavadoras, camiones de bomberos o incluso un tanque. Y aplasta todo fuera […]

summary: Japan: Famitsu's Most Wanted Nintendo Games (June 13th - 19th)
title: Japan: Famitsu's Most Wanted Nintendo Games (June 13th - 19th)
body:
Japan: Famitsu’s Most Wanted Nintendo Games (June 13th – 19th)

Famitsu loves to poll their readers frequently to find out their most wanted Nintendo games. The latest results were posted earlier today. This data is for the week of June 13th to 19th. The top spot for this week, after previously losing it, belongs to Pokemon Sword and Shield once again. Atelier Ryza: Ever Darkness & The Secret Hideout and God Eater 3 are the two new arrivals.
